159\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.159</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ῥεῖ μάλιστα ὁ ἀὴρ ῥέων ἐν τοῖς ὑψηλοῖς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg026:347a:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mete.\">Mete.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">347a34</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg026:349a:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">349a34</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φλὸξ ῥυεῖσα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg061:31\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Brut.\">Brut.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">31</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; so <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὴν Αἴτνην ῥυῆναι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg004:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; esp. of a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">flow</tr_> of words, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀπὸ γλώσσης μέλιτος γλυκίων ῥέεν αὐδή</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:249\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.249</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg001.perseus-grc1:39:97\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a cl